name: Fox & Bunny ( YIN AND YANG )
description: Yin and Yang, love dance of the Fox and the Bunny Many things in our world have their opposite. However, both sides of a phenomenon, a thing, do not exclude one from the other, rather the opposite, one needs the other. Because without night there can be no day, without suffering there is no joy, and without life there is no death. Opposites are inextricably linked, forming a single whole, like two sides of the same coin.
